## Checklist for New Growth Feature

When adding a new metric or growth mechanic:

- [ ] Schema change in `prisma/schema.prisma` (timestamp or counter field)
- [ ] Migration SQL written and reviewed (`prisma/migrations/...`)
- [ ] API route with POST (user action) and GET (admin metrics)
- [ ] Type guards on all inputs (no `any`, validate shapes)
- [ ] Admin dashboard card showing the metric vs target
- [ ] Component for user interaction (modal, form, etc.)
- [ ] Trigger logic in parent page (eligibility check)
- [ ] Session storage for ephemeral state (dismissed today)
- [ ] Database for permanent state (completed ever)
- [ ] Integration guide if external system needs to call API
- [ ] Build test passes (`npm run build`)
- [ ] Update `GROWTH_DEPLOYMENT.md` with testing steps

